data.description: **Motivated sellers and ready for your offers!** Welcome to your spacious dream home, nestled in the embrace of a tranquil country living on expansive 5 acres within the desired equestrian community of Prairie Creek Park. Experience the epitome of freedom and space in this single-family home boasting 2,571 sqft of living space, four bedrooms, and three full bathrooms. This home offers multiple updates, such as a brand-new roof, landscape, new tile flooring, a new AC system, fresh interior and exterior paint, a new paver pool deck with coping, and a recently resurfaced pool, giving the home a contemporary allure. As soon as you step indoors, you will find an open-concept floor plan that accentuates the natural light streaming through abundant windows and sliders. The windows are impact-resistant. You will find stainless steel appliances and plenty of cabinetry space in the kitchen, with updated granite countertops. The expansive master suite offers a generously sized walk-in closet, a walk-in shower, and a separate tub with a large sink for convenience. Find a second bedroom just next door with a private bathroom offering you a choice of primary suites. The other rooms will be located on the side of the home. Enjoy the great outdoors and bring all your toys! This home is fenced for peace and privacy. As soon as you step outside, you will find a large deck to host all your gatherings and a generous pool for all your family and friends to enjoy. For the horse enthusiast, there's a 4-stall barn awaiting your equine companions with water already hooked up. The detached garage provides convenience for storage or parking with an additional small office or exercise room. This home is secluded yet centrally located. This property offers the best of both worlds—tranquility and accessibility. Explore miles of horseback riding trails within the community while being within easy reach of shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Whether it's a trip to downtown Punta Gorda or a drive to nearby cities like Sarasota, Cape Coral, or Fort Myers, this home's location caters to your every need. Discover the lifestyle you've always envisioned—come and experience this remarkable property today. Your dream home awaits!
